      "content": "thanks for explaining. i guess i'm mostly wondering about the \"concerns\" part. i've heard some people say that parents who are worried about this are just being \"uneducated\" or \"bigoted,\" while others say the schools are overstepping. is there actually a valid logical argument from the parents' side, or is it mostly just based on personal or religious beliefs?",
