      "content": "that makes sense. but then on the other side, it feels like the schools are saying they have to do this to prevent bullying and make sure kids who are different feel safe. wouldn't you say that's a more \"objective\" or urgent necessity compared to just a disagreement over values? like, isn't protecting kids from harm a more concrete goal than just following traditional parent rules?",
